Tt c d liu u l kiu s khng c gi tr no b thiu Cc thuc tnh trong d liu gm :

  • density: T trong ca ru
  • pH
  • sulphates
  • alcohol: Nng cn
  • quality : Cht lng

df_cleaned.reset_index(drop=True, inplace=True)

c) Mi quan h gia tng thuc tnh
In[10]:
fig, axes = plt.subplots(4, 3, figsize=(20, 18))
axes = axes.flatten()
feature_cols = [col for col in df_cleaned.columns if col != 'quality']
for i, col in enumerate(feature_cols):
    sns.boxplot(x='quality', y=col, data=df_cleaned, ax=axes[i], color='darkcyan')  # dng color
    axes[i].set_title(f'{col.replace("_"," ").title()} vs. Quality')
    axes[i].set_xlabel('Quality')
    axes[i].set_ylabel(col.replace("_", " ").title())
# n subplot tha
if len(feature_cols) < len(axes):
    for j in range(len(feature_cols), len(axes)):
        axes[j].set_visible(False)
plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

Nhn xt :
+ Xu hng r rng : alcoholtng theo cht lng ru v volatile acidity cng cao th cht lng cng gim
+ Xu hng yu hn : sulphats,citric acid c xu hng tng nh
CC THUC TNH CN LI KHNG C XU HNG R RNG
